        "description": "When rescue seems impossible, were you able to thrive on the islands？This is a sandbox survival building game with high freedom and diverse gameplay.\n\n**Highlights**\n- Exploring islands and searching for treasures，climbing，sailing，rowing，swimming\n- Surviving by gathering resources, building shelter, crafting tools or feeling the sea breeze, enjoying the sunrise and sunset.\n- Hunting for food and managing encounters with aggressive wildlife\n- Planting a variety of vegetables and fruits.\n- Mixing various ingredients to cook delicious meals\n- Building and decorating your big house\n- Capturing animals for breeding and petting\n- Sharing your islands and explore new ones created by others.\n- Playing with your friends, whether it’s exploring, building together or tricking each other, they are all up to you!\n- Customizing the adventures by designing your own\n\nStill there are many interesting things waiting for you to explore!\n\n## Join our *discord* (discord.gg/rU2vg7kcMv) to start the journey!",
